channel.title: My First Model :S
channel.description:
[size=25pt] I have not posted this anywhere else!!![/size]
Well i know that capes are soooo old but i thought as my FIRST EVER model i would try one. (Not from scratch :S) Personely i dont think it is all that good so i have kept it in a "mqo file" so if you wanna make it better insted of using my rubish :D :D but im going to let you be the judge...
